{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 127344, "create_time": 1653009665, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "多看点新闻联播，不要乱想", "timestamp": 1653009665}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 127349, "create_time": 1653009937, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "确实令人忧虑，但是下结论为时尚早\n有太多变量了，清零政策是否长期持续？疫情何时突变？\n\n如果截止到现在，疫情戛然而止，中国的政策还是整体合理的：前两年高效清零，最近两三个月倒行逆施但瑕不掩瑜\n\n所以还是要看后续变化。情况恶化是近两三个月的事情，政策判断往往有滞后性~\n这波应对奥密克戎确实很糟糕，但从某种程度上我还是相信这个政党的自我修复能力，虽然这次修的有点慢", "timestamp": 1653009937}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 127354, "create_time": 1653010040, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Bob: 20大把***选下去，我就相信它的自我修复能力。", "timestamp": 1653010040}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 127356, "create_time": 1653010140, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Bob: 文革修了10年。", "timestamp": 1653010140}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 127357, "create_time": 1653010217, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Bob: 政治局常委会说我国抗疫政策是由党的宗旨和性质决定的。已经开始搞15分钟核酸采样圈、永久性方舱医院。谭德塞说动态清零“没有可持续性”，在国内被屏蔽得干干净净，赵立坚警告说“不要发表不负责任的言论”……\n\n清零政策是否会长期持续，一两个月前我尚且相信会有转机，现在我不相信了，准备润了", "timestamp": 1653010217}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 127359, "create_time": 1653010326, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Bob: 大跃进3年，文化大革命10年，你我的人生还剩大约60年，你确定想拿人生作为赌注？", "timestamp": 1653010326}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": true, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 127364, "create_time": 1653010478, "is_b